title: Boulders is the place to LIVE!
posting_body: ['Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, but close to the energy of downtown—the best of both', 'worlds in Walnut Creek.', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x522', 'From $2,792', '.', '2 Bed 1 Bath .', '825 Sq.', 'Ft', '* Unit 504B - Available Now', '* Unit 520D - Available Now', 'Boulders', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Address:', '530 North Civic Drive Walnut Creek, CA 94596', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Make this two-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment at The Boulders your next home.', 'When you step inside this sophisticated residence, you will discover an expansive living area with laminate wood-style flooring in some floorplans.', 'The kitchen features stainless steel GE appliances as well as granite counters and white cabinets that add elegance to the space.', 'You will appreciate the Maytag front-load washer and dryer combo as well.', 'Select homes also feature dual-pane windows and spacious walk-in closets.', 'Outside your doorstep, the community offers an array of exciting amenities including two heated swimming pools, which are available year-round.', 'You can also enjoy a cookout with your neighbors in the grilling area.', 'Additionally, the community is located within a mile from BART, making your daily commute more convenient.', 'For additional details, call today.', 'FLOORPLAN/UNIT\u2002 \u2002FEATURES', 'Interior Courtyard', 'Off Street', 'Washer and Dryer', 'Upstairs', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'Sunday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x522', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
